Author: Azaryxe
Text: I'm not getting up quite as early, but I love running on Sunday mornings because it is pretty much desolate until 10am. I've found the more I've gone running, the less anxious I feel about others seeing me. I still get some anxiety though.

Author: grossenten98
Text: Oh I used to look ridiculous, I’d wake up to walk at 3:30 and go until 6am so I could get my step goal finished before anyone was awake. Then I would double my step goal by walking normally throughout the day.   It’s crazy stuff but it sure is relaxing to get up and about in the morning
